  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Bento Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bento Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#0A0E1A] text-[#F1F5F9] font-sans overflow-hidden flex flex-col p-6\\\">\\n  <!-- HEADER SECTION -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6 bg-[#111827] rounded-2xl border border-[#1e293b] p-4 shadow-2xl shadow-cyan-900/20\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00D4FF] to-[#8B5CF6] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,212,255,0.4)]\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-2xl\\\">\360\237\244\226</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase leading-none\\\">AI ACADEMY</h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94A3B8] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase\\\">Interactive Learning Portal</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 mx-12\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-1 px-1\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-bold text-[#00D4FF]\\\">PROGRESS TO LEVEL 2</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-mono\\\">750 / 1000 XP</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"h-3 w-full bg-[#1e293b] rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-[#334155]\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"h-full w-[75%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00D4FF] via-[#8B5CF6] to-[#00D4FF] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,212,255,0.5)]\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94A3B8] uppercase\\\">Current Rank</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#F59E0B]\\\">Lv. 1 AI Newbie</div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#F59E0B] flex items-center justify-center bg-[#F59E0B]/10\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg font-black text-[#F59E0B]\\\">1</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex gap-6 min-h-0\\\">\\n    <!-- LEFT: GAME HUB (BENTO GRID) -->\\n    <main class=\\\"flex-[2.5] grid grid-cols-3 grid-rows-3 gap-4\\\">\\n      <!-- Game 1: Neuron Builder -->\\n      <div class=\\\"row-span-2 col-span-1 bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#00D4FF]/30 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#00D4FF] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-[#00D4FF]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl\\\"></div>\\n        <div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#00D4FF]/20 border border-[#00D4FF]/50 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4\\\">\360\237\247\240</div>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\\\">Neuron Builder</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed italic\\\">Connect the synapses! Learn how Neural Networks process data through hidden layers.</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-[#00D4FF]/10 text-[#00D4FF] text-[10px] font-bold rounded uppercase border border-[#00D4FF]/20\\\">Hard</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94A3B8] italic\\\">+250 XP</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 2: Data Sorter -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-2 bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#8B5CF6]/30 p-6 flex items-center gap-6 relative overflow-hidden hover:border-[#8B5CF6] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#8B5CF6]/20 border border-[#8B5CF6]/50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-5xl\\\">\360\237\223\212</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\\\">Data Sorter</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#94A3B8]\\\">Master the art of Data Labeling. Spot biases, clean noisy sets, and train your model to perfection.</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-4 mt-3\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex -space-x-2\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500 border border-white\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500 border border-white\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500 border border-white\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94A3B8] self-center\\\">Join 1.2k players</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 3: Prompt Wizard -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-cyan-500/30 p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center justify-center hover:border-cyan-400 transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl mb-2\\\">\360\237\252\204</div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Prompt Wizard</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#94A3B8] mt-1\\\">Craft the perfect spell for LLMs</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 4: Model Showdown -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#10B981]/30 p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center justify-center hover:border-[#10B981] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl mb-2\\\">\342\232\224\357\270\217</div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Model Showdown</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#94A3B8] mt-1\\\">Classify, Regress, or Cluster?</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 5: Overfitting Escape -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-2 bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#F59E0B]/30 p-6 flex items-center justify-between relative overflow-hidden hover:border-[#F59E0B] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"z-10\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\\\">Overfitting Escape</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#94A3B8] max-w-[300px]\\\">Navigate the validation maze! Don\'t let your model memorize the answers.</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-5xl opacity-80 z-10\\\">\360\237\232\250</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1/2 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#F59E0B]/5 to-transparent\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 6: Ethical AI Judge -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#EF4444]/30 p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center justify-center hover:border-[#EF4444] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl mb-2\\\">\342\232\226\357\270\217</div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Ethical Judge</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#94A3B8] mt-1\\\">Balance fairness & transparency</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </main>\\n\\n    <!-- RIGHT: SIDEBAR (STATS & AIKO) -->\\n    <aside class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-[280px]\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border border-[#1e293b] p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-[#94A3B8] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#00D4FF]\\\"></span> Recent Achievements\\n        </h4>\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-2 bg-[#0A0E1A] rounded-xl border border-[#1e293b]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xl\\\">\360\237\247\240</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">First Neuron</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[9px] text-[#94A3B8]\\\">Build your first network</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-2 bg-[#0A0E1A] rounded-xl border border-[#1e293b]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xl\\\">\360\237\224\245</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">On Fire</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[9px] text-[#94A3B8]\\\">10 correct labels in 30s</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-2 opacity-30 grayscale\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xl\\\">\360\237\217\206</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">AI Master</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[9px] text-[#94A3B8]\\\">Complete all 6 challenges</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-auto\\\">\\n          <h4 class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#94A3B8] uppercase mb-2\\\">Daily Quest</h4>\\n          <div class=\\\"p-3 bg-[#00D4FF]/5 border border-[#00D4FF]/20 rounded-xl\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#00D4FF] leading-snug\\\">Clean 50 data points in \'Data Sorter\' to earn a Mega Pack!</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- AIKO MASCOT CHAT -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-[#8B5CF6] to-[#6D28D9] rounded-3xl p-5 relative overflow-hidden shadow-xl\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 opacity-20\\\">\\n            <svg width=\\\"120\\\" height=\\\"120\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"white\\\"><path d=\\\"M12 2c5.523 0 10 4.477 10 10s-4.477 10-10 10-10-4.477-10-10 4.477-10 10-10zm0 2c-4.411 0-8 3.589-8 8s3.589 8 8 8 8-3.589 8-8-3.589-8-8-8zm0 3c2.757 0 5 2.243 5 5h-2c0-1.654-1.346-3-3-3s-3 1.346-3 3h-2c0-2.757 2.243-5 5-5z\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"relative z-10 flex flex-col gap-3\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-2xl\\\">\360\237\230\212</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-xs bg-white/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">AIKO GUIDE</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm font-medium leading-tight\\\">\\\"Waduh, overfitting nih! Bayangin kamu hafalin semua soal ujian, tapi pas soalnya beda dikit langsung blank. Itu yang terjadi sama modelmu!\\\"</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </aside>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <!-- FOOTER -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"mt-6 flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] text-[#94A3B8] font-mono border-t border-[#1e293b] pt-4\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <span>SYSTEM: <span class=\\\"text-[#00D4FF]\\\">ONLINE</span></span>\\n      <span>LATENCY: <span class=\\\"text-[#10B981]\\\">12ms</span></span>\\n      <span>DATASET: <span class=\\\"text-[#8B5CF6]\\\">V.4.2</span></span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"hover:text-white cursor-pointer transition-colors\\\">SUPPORT</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"hover:text-white cursor-pointer transition-colors text-white font-bold\\\">SHARE PROGRESS \342\206\227</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Bento Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bento Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#0A0E1A] text-[#F1F5F9] font-sans overflow-hidden flex flex-col p-6\\\">\\n  <!-- HEADER SECTION -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6 bg-[#111827] rounded-2xl border border-[#1e293b] p-4 shadow-2xl shadow-cyan-900/20\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00D4FF] to-[#8B5CF6] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,212,255,0.4)]\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-2xl\\\">\360\237\244\226</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase leading-none\\\">AI ACADEMY</h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94A3B8] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase\\\">Interactive Learning Portal</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 mx-12\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-end mb-1 px-1\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-bold text-[#00D4FF]\\\">PROGRESS TO LEVEL 2</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-[11px] font-mono\\\">750 / 1000 XP</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"h-3 w-full bg-[#1e293b] rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-[#334155]\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"h-full w-[75%] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00D4FF] via-[#8B5CF6] to-[#00D4FF] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,212,255,0.5)]\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94A3B8] uppercase\\\">Current Rank</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#F59E0B]\\\">Lv. 1 AI Newbie</div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-[#F59E0B] flex items-center justify-center bg-[#F59E0B]/10\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-lg font-black text-[#F59E0B]\\\">1</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex gap-6 min-h-0\\\">\\n    <!-- LEFT: GAME HUB (BENTO GRID) -->\\n    <main class=\\\"flex-[2.5] grid grid-cols-3 grid-rows-3 gap-4\\\">\\n      <!-- Game 1: Neuron Builder -->\\n      <div class=\\\"row-span-2 col-span-1 bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#00D4FF]/30 p-6 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#00D4FF] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-[#00D4FF]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl\\\"></div>\\n        <div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#00D4FF]/20 border border-[#00D4FF]/50 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4\\\">\360\237\247\240</div>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-2\\\">Neuron Builder</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#94A3B8] leading-relaxed italic\\\">Connect the synapses! Learn how Neural Networks process data through hidden layers.</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-[#00D4FF]/10 text-[#00D4FF] text-[10px] font-bold rounded uppercase border border-[#00D4FF]/20\\\">Hard</span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94A3B8] italic\\\">+250 XP</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 2: Data Sorter -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-2 bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#8B5CF6]/30 p-6 flex items-center gap-6 relative overflow-hidden hover:border-[#8B5CF6] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-24 h-24 bg-[#8B5CF6]/20 border border-[#8B5CF6]/50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-5xl\\\">\360\237\223\212</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\\\">Data Sorter</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#94A3B8]\\\">Master the art of Data Labeling. Spot biases, clean noisy sets, and train your model to perfection.</p>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-4 mt-3\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex -space-x-2\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-500 border border-white\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-500 border border-white\\\"></div>\\n              <div class=\\\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-500 border border-white\\\"></div>\\n            </div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94A3B8] self-center\\\">Join 1.2k players</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 3: Prompt Wizard -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-cyan-500/30 p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center justify-center hover:border-cyan-400 transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl mb-2\\\">\360\237\252\204</div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Prompt Wizard</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#94A3B8] mt-1\\\">Craft the perfect spell for LLMs</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 4: Model Showdown -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#10B981]/30 p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center justify-center hover:border-[#10B981] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl mb-2\\\">\342\232\224\357\270\217</div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Model Showdown</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#94A3B8] mt-1\\\">Classify, Regress, or Cluster?</p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 5: Overfitting Escape -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-2 bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#F59E0B]/30 p-6 flex items-center justify-between relative overflow-hidden hover:border-[#F59E0B] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"z-10\\\">\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-xl font-bold mb-1\\\">Overfitting Escape</h3>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#94A3B8] max-w-[300px]\\\">Navigate the validation maze! Don\'t let your model memorize the answers.</p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-5xl opacity-80 z-10\\\">\360\237\232\250</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1/2 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#F59E0B]/5 to-transparent\\\"></div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Game 6: Ethical AI Judge -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border-2 border-[#EF4444]/30 p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center justify-center hover:border-[#EF4444] transition-all\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl mb-2\\\">\342\232\226\357\270\217</div>\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Ethical Judge</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#94A3B8] mt-1\\\">Balance fairness & transparency</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </main>\\n\\n    <!-- RIGHT: SIDEBAR (STATS & AIKO) -->\\n    <aside class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col gap-4 min-w-[280px]\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#111827] rounded-3xl border border-[#1e293b] p-5 flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h4 class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-[#94A3B8] uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-1 h-3 bg-[#00D4FF]\\\"></span> Recent Achievements\\n        </h4>\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-2 bg-[#0A0E1A] rounded-xl border border-[#1e293b]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xl\\\">\360\237\247\240</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">First Neuron</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[9px] text-[#94A3B8]\\\">Build your first network</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-2 bg-[#0A0E1A] rounded-xl border border-[#1e293b]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xl\\\">\360\237\224\245</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">On Fire</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[9px] text-[#94A3B8]\\\">10 correct labels in 30s</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 p-2 opacity-30 grayscale\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"text-xl\\\">\360\237\217\206</div>\\n            <div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">AI Master</div>\\n              <div class=\\\"text-[9px] text-[#94A3B8]\\\">Complete all 6 challenges</div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-auto\\\">\\n          <h4 class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#94A3B8] uppercase mb-2\\\">Daily Quest</h4>\\n          <div class=\\\"p-3 bg-[#00D4FF]/5 border border-[#00D4FF]/20 rounded-xl\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#00D4FF] leading-snug\\\">Clean 50 data points in \'Data Sorter\' to earn a Mega Pack!</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- AIKO MASCOT CHAT -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-gradient-to-br from-[#8B5CF6] to-[#6D28D9] rounded-3xl p-5 relative overflow-hidden shadow-xl\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 opacity-20\\\">\\n            <svg width=\\\"120\\\" height=\\\"120\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" fill=\\\"white\\\"><path d=\\\"M12 2c5.523 0 10 4.477 10 10s-4.477 10-10 10-10-4.477-10-10 4.477-10 10-10zm0 2c-4.411 0-8 3.589-8 8s3.589 8 8 8 8-3.589 8-8-3.589-8-8-8zm0 3c2.757 0 5 2.243 5 5h-2c0-1.654-1.346-3-3-3s-3 1.346-3 3h-2c0-2.757 2.243-5 5-5z\\\"/></svg>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"relative z-10 flex flex-col gap-3\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"text-2xl\\\">\360\237\230\212</span>\\n            <span class=\\\"font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-xs bg-white/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">AIKO GUIDE</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-sm font-medium leading-tight\\\">\\\"Waduh, overfitting nih! Bayangin kamu hafalin semua soal ujian, tapi pas soalnya beda dikit langsung blank. Itu yang terjadi sama modelmu!\\\"</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </aside>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <!-- FOOTER -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"mt-6 flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] text-[#94A3B8] font-mono border-t border-[#1e293b] pt-4\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-6\\\">\\n      <span>SYSTEM: <span class=\\\"text-[#00D4FF]\\\">ONLINE</span></span>\\n      <span>LATENCY: <span class=\\\"text-[#10B981]\\\">12ms</span></span>\\n      <span>DATASET: <span class=\\\"text-[#8B5CF6]\\\">V.4.2</span></span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"hover:text-white cursor-pointer transition-colors\\\">SUPPORT</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"hover:text-white cursor-pointer transition-colors text-white font-bold\\\">SHARE PROGRESS \342\206\227</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
