    modified_response: "I am creating `/src/components/PromptWizard.tsx` to build Game 3 (\"Prompt Wizard\") mapping out the principles of Prompt Engineering. It uses highly interactive block builders ([ROLE], [TASK], [FORMAT], [CONSTRAINT]) where players click/build synergistic lines inside a magic wand container, click \"Cast Spell\" with glitter outcomes, and view instant side-by-side comparison tables. It integrates achievement badges to motivate the players."
