  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Assessing Perfection In Build**\n\nThe production build was, as expected, a resounding success! I\'m now cross-referencing the final build against the user\'s initial instructions. Specifically, the Bento Grid theme\'s styling, colors, and layout patterns are all perfect. The UI appears to have been developed exactly as designed.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed building the **AI Arena - Educational AI Engineering Portal** Web App, completely optimized with a high-fidelity **Bento Grid Design Theme**. \n\nHere is a summary of the achievements and the premium features implemented:\n\n### \360\237\216\256 The 6 Immersive Mini-Games\n1. **Neuron Builder \360\237\247\240**: Players connect glowing neuron structures across Input, Hidden, and Output layers via direct user-driven SVG connection nodes. Features real-time **Network Strength** calculations and a visual Boss Evaluation challenge in Indonesian about Underfitting.\n2. **Data Sorter \360\237\223\212**: A high-velocity data curation game designed within a vintage Polaroid theme. Teaches about multi-labeling bias and data corruption, prompting players to label clean data or `FLAG/SKIP` ambiguous, incorrect, or corrupted inputs.\n3. **Prompt Wizard \360\237\252\204**: A holographic sorcerer workspace where players combine `[ROLE]`, `[TASK]`, `[FORMAT]`, and `[CONSTRAINT]` blocks to cast a precise engineering spell on the language model, displaying side-by-side output evaluations.\n4. **Model Showdown \342\232\224\357\270\217**: Fast-paced trading card matches challenging players to pitch different model categories (Classification, Regression, or Clustering) against specialized industrial real-world tasks.\n5. **Overfitting Escape \360\237\232\250**: An interactive HTML Canvas-based fitting simulator. Players slide a Complexity slider to render underfitting, balanced generalization, or wild overfitting curve trajectories\342\200\224watching a cute AIKO robot navigate coordinates and hit obstacles.\n6. **Ethical AI Judge \342\232\226\357\270\217**: Put on the courtroom wig! Players review Automated Bank Credit bots or HR Recruiter models for structural historical bias, gender discriminants, or geographical redlining.\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual Theme & Interactive Mechanics\n- **Bento Core Grid UI**: Encased inside neon card borders (`--neon-blue`, `--neon-purple`, `--neon-green`, `--neon-orange`, `--neon-red`), CRT monitor glow overlays, interactive progress selectors, and highly aesthetic display layouts.\n- **Mascot AIKO Guide \360\237\230\212 \360\237\244\224 \360\237\216\211**: AIKO acts as an integrated assistant in the viewport, responding with customized speech triggers, funny AI jokes, and instant contextual validation tips dependent on the current game session state.\n- **Unified XP & Progression Engine**: Feeds cumulative XP through standard checkpoints (Level 1\342\200\2236) representing ranks from *AI Newbie* to *AI Ethicist*. Includes structured progress animations.\n- **Native Web Audio SFX**: A stateless custom sound engine synthesizes high-quality sound feedback (hover click plucks, crisp synaptical connection clicks, successful spell arpeggios, wrong buzz sweeps, and level-up congratulations waves) by calling browser-native Web Audio API audio oscillators.\n- **Persistent Local Cache**: Uses `localStorage` to preserve progress, total accumulated XP, list of completed mini-games, and unlocked badges across user sessions.\n- **12 Achievement Badges**:\n  - \360\237\247\240 **First Neuron** - Build your first neural network.\n  - \360\237\223\212 **Clean Labeling** - Accurately label training nodes.\n  - \360\237\252\204 **Prompt Engineer** - Design a 100% complete prompt formula.\n  - \360\237\233\241\357\270\217 **Model Knight** - Achieve answers streak on Model Showdown.\n  - \360\237\214\252\357\270\217 **Escape Master** - Generalize the model curve correctly.\n  - \342\232\226\357\270\217 **AI Ethicist** - Solve all ethical courtroom dilemmas.\n  - \360\237\217\206 **AI Academy Graduate** - Complete all 6 challenges.\n  - \360\237\221\221 **Scholar Elite** - Surpass Level 3 milestone.\n  - \360\237\224\245 **Streak Burner** - Correctly answer 5 questions in a row.\n  - \360\237\216\265 **Oscillator Sound** - Activate sound effects.\n  - \360\237\247\271 **Anti-Bias Cleaner** - Successfully flag noise points in the dataset.\n  - \360\237\216\223 **AI Master Scholar** - Reach Level 6.\n"
    thinking_duration {
