    thinking: "**Verifying Final Outcome**\n\nI\'m thrilled! Both `compile_applet` and `lint_applet` have completed flawlessly. Now, I\'m verifying all aspects. The user\'s initial feedback about the UI has been addressed. I\'ve polished the layout and added \"gorgeous\" to the UI! I believe we have successfully satisfied all requests!\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have successfully finalized a massive UI overhaul and introduced the brand new premium training feature you requested! Here is a summary of the accomplishments:\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual Identity & UI Polishing\n* **Glassmorphism Theme System**: Infused all component backings with high-end glass structures (`glass`), depth borders, and hover micro-animations that respond organically to cursors.\n* **Responsive Bento Layout**: Beautifully balanced row and column spans on all viewports, maximizing typography contrast and spacing.\n* **Glow Settings & Asset Alignment**: Added glowing color borders matching each mini-game\'s specific theme (deep cyan for Neuron Builder, violet for Data Sorter, green for Model Showdown, etc.).\n* **Holographic Scanlines**: Retained the subtle terminal scanner look on overlays to keep the interactive game atmosphere immersive.\n\n### \360\237\216\233\357\270\217 New Feature: Model Tuner & Playground (Hyperparameter Sandbox)\n* **Real-time LLM controls**: Added an interactive 7th Bento Module! Students can now slide parameters directly:\n  1. **Temperature (Suhu)**: View how cheap, deterministic responses transform into creative, wild hallucinations.\n  2. **Top-P (Nucleus)**: Restrict vocabulary lists to understand sampling parameters.\n  3. **Frequency Penalty**: Test negative values to see AI fall into infinite repetition loops!\n* **Multi-model emulation**: Simulated outputs from top arsitekturs (e.g., Google **Gemini-3.5-Flash** speed outputs and **DeepSeek-R1** visible step-by-step reasoning chains!).\n* **System Prompt Injector**: Includes presets like **Meow Persona Kucing Anggora**, **Motivator Coach Gym**, and **Cyber Hacker 1337** to observe personality shifts in real-time.\n* **Progress Claim**: Awards a whopping **+250 XP** upon completing playground trials!\n\n### \360\237\244\226 Expanded Mascot Companion (AIKO Bot)\n* **Dynamic Information Grids**: Re-engineered the \"\360\237\222\241 Minta Teori\" and \"\342\234\250 Joke AI\" buttons so AIKO randomly pulls from an array of professional machine learning theories (e.g., Dropout networks, Sigmoid functions, Garbage-In Garbage-Out, activation thresholds) and hilarious machine learning jokes!\n"
